frameDefinitions: An Entity survives a situation with some Support, which tends to be far below the accustomed or standard level expected.
The LUs in this frame refer to biological entities other than human beings and plants, which are labeled by the FE Animal.  ''  'My husband and I adopted a really sweet dog last year.'
A Survivor manages to avoid being negatively affected, despite encountering a Dangerous_situation.
The frame concerns the vehicles that human beings use for the purpose of transportation.
The Noise_maker is an artifact used to produce sound, especially for musical effect.

listRoleDefinitions: The living organism which requires the <fen>Support</fen> to survive.
The resource that the <fen>Entity</fen> relies on to survive through a situation.
The living organism belonging to the kingdom Animalia.
The <fen>Dangerous_situation</fen> is one in which people are likely or expected to be negatively affected.
The time at which the surviving takes place.
The location where the <fen>Survivor</fen> (primarily) lives during the <fen>Dangerous_situation</fen>.
Vehicle is the transportation device that the human beings use to travel.This role is incorporated into each LU in this frame.
This role identifies the entity or substance that is designed to produce sound.
